I believe that it is a great start, but there are some issues that can easily be resolved: the Jeep is slower than the fire engine at top speed (not sure why), plus the Jeep keeps spinning out if you turn at high speed, no matter how hard you turn it. Finally, all the text that is in the icons at the top needs to be a different colour as its hard to read. Some minor complaints that don't overly matter, but it would be nice to see an update that solves those issues. Thanks!
